<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>There's a really easy mental shortcut engineers or engineers who are aspiring entrepreneurs can make.<p>It starts with a thought like: "Oh, I can do that by gluing together X, Y, and Z and configuring the foobaz widget to sync via the 802.11q network."<p>Your second thought should be: "No normal person could do that, and even those who could probably wouldn't want to."</font></span><p><font size=1><u><a href="reply?id=3527615&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%67%43%6f%77%50%69%71%37%50%73">reply</a></u></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=120></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_3527825 href="vote?for=3527825&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%67%43%6f%77%50%69%71%37%50%73"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_3527825></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=TeMPOraL">TeMPOraL</a> 6 days ago  | <a href="item?id=3527825">link</a></span></div><br>
